{"title":"Steam","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Steam","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.30](/0.30 \"0.30\")**: This article **may not be** up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of Crawl.*\n\n**Steam** is one of the least common elemental forces you will encounter as you explore the [Dungeon](/Dungeon \"Dungeon\"). Unlike most elements, it is very difficult for most characters to have access to steam, and few monsters are even capable of it.\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 Steam Clouds](#Steam_Clouds)\n- [2 Steam Damage](#Steam_Damage)\n- [3 Resistance](#Resistance)\n  - [3.1 Vulnerability](#Vulnerability)\n- [4 History](#History)\n- [5 See Also](#See_Also)\n\n## Steam Clouds\n\nSteam [clouds](/Cloud \"Cloud\") are created when beams of [fire](/Fire \"Fire\") travel over [water](/Water \"Water\"), or when beams of [cold](/Cold \"Cold\") travel over [lava](/Lava \"Lava\"). Examples of fiery beams include the [wand of flame](/Wand_of_flame \"Wand of flame\"), [Flame Wave](/Flame_Wave \"Flame Wave\"), and [Fireball](/Fireball \"Fireball\"). The player cannot create any ice projectiles, but monsters like [frost giants](/Frost_giant \"Frost giant\") can use [Throw Frost](/Throw_Frost \"Throw Frost\") or [Bolt of Cold](/Bolt_of_Cold \"Bolt of Cold\"). They are also created by the [Steam Ball](/Steam_Ball \"Steam Ball\") spell.\n\nSteam clouds deal [steam damage](#Steam_Damage). In addition, they are [opaque](/Cloud#Opaque \"Cloud\"); having 2 or more steam clouds in a given direction will block [line of sight](/Line_of_sight \"Line of sight\").\n\n## Steam Damage\n\nSteam damage is one of the rarest elements in the game. It appears from the following sources:\n\n- steam clouds\n- the [Steam Ball](/Steam_Ball \"Steam Ball\") spell\n\n## Resistance\n\nSteam resistance (rSteam) prevents steam clouds from doing any damage, and reduces the impact damage from Steam Ball by -66%.\n\nThe following sources provide dedicated steam resistance:\n\n- [steam dragon scales](/Steam_dragon_scales \"Steam dragon scales\")\n- [Dragonskin cloak](/Dragonskin_cloak \"Dragonskin cloak\")\n- being a pale [draconian](/Draconian \"Draconian\")\n\nIn addition, having any amount of [fire resistance](/Fire_resistance \"Fire resistance\") (rF+ or higher) grants steam resistance. You must actually have rF+, so [Mummies](/Mummies \"Mummies\") with a [ring of fire](/Ring_of_fire \"Ring of fire\") won't get steam resistance.\n\n### Vulnerability\n\nAny amount of fire vulnerability also gives steam vulnerability, which increases all steam damage by +50%.\n\n## History\n\n- Prior to [0.14](/0.14 \"0.14\"), there were 3 levels of rSteam. Having any amount of rSteam gave immunity to steam clouds; having more levels only reduced impact damage from steam-related spells.\n- Prior to [0.13](/0.13 \"0.13\"), [fire](/Fire \"Fire\") vulnerability did not give you steam vulnerability.\n\n## See Also\n\n[List of steam resistant monsters](/Category:Steam_resistance \"Category:Steam resistance\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Steam - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Steam\",\"wgTitle\":\"Steam\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":74993,\"wgRevisionId\":74993,\"wgArticleId\":3385,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.30 articles\",\"Threats\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"Febr